Package: bx3-design-theme
Version: 1.0.0
Section: gnome
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: gnome-shell (>= 40), gtk-3.0, libgtk-3-0
Maintainer: Bxthre3 Inc <dev@bxthre3.com>
Description: BX3 Design System - GTK Theme Package
 Adaptive, accessible theme system for Linux desktops.
 Supports AgentOS, Zo Space, VPC, and Irrig8 variants.
 Features automatic accessibility detection and runtime switching.
Homepage: https://github.com/bxthre3inc/bx3-integrations